      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "<h2>Kafka / Streams metrics</h2><p>這頁先看 runtime metrics，不看 benchmark artifact。Prometheus 會抓 Redpanda 與 Kafka Streams JVM metrics。</p><pre>HTTP app/direct_kafka\n  -> inventory.seckill.requested\n  -> Kafka Streams source consumer\n  -> processValues(FixedKeyProcessor)\n  -> RocksDB inventory-store + dedupe-store\n  -> retry: requeue to inventory.seckill.requested\n  -> final outcome: inventory.seckill.result\n  -> async sink (PG compatibility only)</pre><p><strong>怎麼讀下面的圖：</strong></p><ul><li><code>records consumed/sec</code> = worker 從 <code>inventory.seckill.requested</code> 吃進來的速率</li><li><code>stream thread process/sec</code> = Streams thread 內部 <code>process()</code> 呼叫速率</li><li><code>result records sent/sec</code> = worker 寫到 <code>inventory.seckill.result</code> 的速率</li><li><code>request topic lag max</code> = input topic 是否堆積</li><li>Redpanda panels 看 broker produce/fetch request rate 與平均 latency</li></ul>",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.1.1",
      "title": "Overview",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 8
      },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum(rate(redpanda_kafka_handler_latency_seconds_count{handler=\"produce\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "produce req/sec",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum(rate(redpanda_kafka_handler_latency_seconds_count{handler=\"fetch\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "fetch req/sec",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Redpanda Request Rate",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ms"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 8
      },
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "1000 * (sum(rate(redpanda_kafka_handler_latency_seconds_sum{handler=\"fetch\"}[$__rate_interval])) / clamp_min(sum(rate(redpanda_kafka_handler_latency_seconds_count{handler=\"fetch\"}[$__rate_interval])), 1))",
          "legendFormat": "fetch latency avg",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "1000 * (sum(rate(redpanda_kafka_handler_latency_seconds_sum{handler=\"produce\"}[$__rate_interval])) / clamp_min(sum(rate(redpanda_kafka_handler_latency_seconds_count{handler=\"produce\"}[$__rate_interval])), 1))",
          "legendFormat": "produce latency avg",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Redpanda Request Latency",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ops"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 16
      },
      "id": 4,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum(kafka_consumer_consumer_fetch_manager_metrics_records_consumed_rate{topic=\"inventory.seckill.requested\"})",
          "legendFormat": "input records consumed/sec",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum(kafka_streams_stream_thread_metrics_process_rate)",
          "legendFormat": "stream thread process/sec",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum(kafka_producer_producer_topic_metrics_record_send_rate{topic=\"inventory.seckill.result\"})",
          "legendFormat": "result records sent/sec",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Kafka Streams Throughput",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 16
      },
      "id": 5,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "max(kafka_consumer_consumer_fetch_manager_metrics_records_lag_max{topic=\"inventory.seckill.requested\"})",
          "legendFormat": "request topic lag max",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "max(kafka_streams_stream_metrics_alive_stream_threads)",
          "legendFormat": "alive stream threads",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "max(kafka_streams_stream_metrics_failed_stream_threads)",
          "legendFormat": "failed stream threads",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Lag and Worker Health",
      "type": "timeseries"
    }
  ],
  "refresh": "5s",
